## Primitive.Name type

The possible names of primitive types returned by the `typeof` operator.

**Signature:**

```typescript
type Name = keyof Map;
```
**References:** [Map](./toolkit.primitive.map.md)

## Example


```ts
type A = Primitive.Name; // "bigint" | "boolean" | "function" | "number" | "object" | "string" | "symbol" | "undefined";
```
